## 🏢 Business Gathering

### Challenge: **RSAConference**

[**RSAC Conference Home**](https://www.rsaconference.com/)

#### What is RSA Conference?

One of the largest and most influential cybersecurity conferences in the world, focusing on cybersecurity, information security, risk management, and privacy. It is attended by global leaders from both technical and executive security roles.

| Category | Details |
| --- | --- |
| **Locations** | San Francisco (Main), Singapore (Asia), Abu Dhabi (Middle East) |
| **Frequency** | Held annually with region-specific schedules |
| **Core Topics** | Network Security, Cloud Security, Application Security, AI, Threat Intelligence, Incident Response, Zero Trust, GRC, Cryptography, Data Privacy |

#### Conference Activities

- **Keynote Speeches:** Insights from global cybersecurity leaders.

- **Technical Sessions:** Ranging from beginner to advanced levels.

- **Hands-on Workshops:** Interactive labs and skill-building.

- **Panel Discussions:** Emerging threats and strategies.

- **Live Demonstrations:** Real-world case studies.

- **Innovation Zones:** Startup showcases.

#### Participating Organizations

- **Tech Giants:** Google, Microsoft, Cisco, Palo Alto Networks, Fortinet, CrowdStrike, IBM, AWS.

- **Others:** Government and enterprise security organizations.

#### Audience

- Security Engineers, SOC Analysts, Penetration Testers, Researchers, CISOs, CTOs, Managers, Consultants, and Students.

#### Importance & Educational Value

- Provides insight into the latest cyber threats and attack techniques.

- Bridges the gap between technical security and business risk.

- Valuable for certifications: **CISSP, CEH, Security+, CCNA/CCNP Security**.

