## 🏴‍☠️ Hackers Gathering

### Challenge: **DEFCON**

[**The Dark Tangent - defcon.org**](https://defcon.org/)

#### What is DEF CON?

The world’s largest and most famous hacker conference. It has a strong focus on offensive security, hacking, and hands-on learning, rooted in underground hacker culture.

| Category | Details |
| --- | --- |
| **Location** | Las Vegas, Nevada, USA |
| **Time** | Annually in August (usually after Black Hat USA) |
| **Registration** | **Cash-only** (emphasizes privacy and anonymity) |

#### Unique Characteristics

- Minimal corporate branding; strong hacker ethics and community-driven culture.

- **Who Attends:** Hackers, Pen Testers, Red Teamers, Reverse Engineers, Malware Analysts, Researchers, Government Professionals, and Hobbyists.

#### Main Topics & Villages

- **Topics:** Web hacking, Network exploitation, Malware, Reverse engineering, Cryptography, Hardware hacking, Wireless attacks, Social engineering, OSINT, Physical security.

- **Villages:** Specialized areas like Web Hacking, Red Team, Blue Team, IoT, AI, Cloud, Lockpicking, and Social Engineering.

#### Capture The Flag (CTF)

Hosts some of the hardest and most prestigious CTF competitions worldwide, often referred to as the **"Hacker Olympics."**

#### Reputation & Impact

- Sets trends in offensive security research.

- Influences tools, techniques, and methodologies used worldwide.

- Bridges underground research with professional cybersecurity.

